  "descriptionTemplate": "\"24\" gains [Energy:Arg1] Aliemus. {Rouse}:\n{Chaos}: The Crit. Rate and Crit. DMG of \"24\" +[StateArg4]%. Each time a Posse is used, the Exalt DMG of \"24\" +[StateArg1].\n{Aequor}: The DMG \"24\" deals enjoys a [StateArg2]% {Tentacle DMG} bonus and inflicts {Poison} equal to 10% of DMG dealt. \"24\"'s Exalt can trigger 50% {Poison} on enemies.\n{Caro}: For every 1 Arithmetica \"24\" consumes, {Embryo Fusion} +5%, \"24\" gains [StateArg3] {STR}.\n{Ultra}: The DMG \"24\" deals enjoys a [StateArg5]% {Counter} DMG Bonus. Shuffle 1 \"Insight\" into the Discard Pile at turn end, Hand Limit +2.",
